{"tid":2066772,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你會唔會咁好心提醒你同事？","createTime":"2020-06-16T13:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T04:04:31.000Z","uid":130466,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"27ed4f4644a06a299ccf3f31856799b528d73e89","tid":2066772,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"同事成日做錯左，有同事發現執左佢手尾，但會周圍同人講佢做野唔小心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他人都知，但就係做野唔小乜果個唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你會提佢叫佢細心翻定理撚得佢死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e42ea8602a288f0e065571014df61f430843401","tid":2066772,"uid":50744,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"十年前會<br />\n而家唔會"},{"pid":"b77109dbec5f1a5db7641f1090cff86ce7b51460","tid":2066772,"uid":212144,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"提，當積陰德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d646f3cc1c7e72c2efce4688ee8612b07279e2d","tid":2066772,"uid":118945,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"好心著雷劈<br />\n一陣佢當你老屎忽<br />\n同時講佢壞話嘅人會話你懶好心"},{"pid":"335539b04d876efc12da291c4d8f9c1ef16bd67c","tid":2066772,"uid":120123,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"都會提返佢。大家出來做野姐.....<br />\n無謂玩到好似宮心計咁。"},{"pid":"2b2f5c64a6716800adbac3a4b0131241fedcf291","tid":2066772,"uid":29093,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:16:40.000Z","msg":"好睇人地係咩 rank <br />\n<br />\n如果人地 rank 高過你,  啲人多數唔敢提 扮唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果人地 rank 低過你,  啲人多數唔會提, 直接屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果人地 rank 同你一樣,  睇關係 , 自己性格 / 人地性格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a293c7c03456e1e0ca9447eb45636c9554b3b4b2","tid":2066772,"uid":175346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ab0694e7ba12127a2762d4f263c9a3de777e515","tid":2066772,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"如果無嘢忙緊就會提."},{"pid":"4aea02c56c904882e75d112e7618f735ea6c3dfd","tid":2066772,"uid":311223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"睇你想多一個朋友定多一個敵人"},{"pid":"87689c1e4e2e3da5125b8a3dc4eef0988c6c12ef","tid":2066772,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4aea02c56c904882e75d112e7618f735ea6c3dfd","tid":2066772,"uid":311223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"睇你想多一個朋友定多一個敵人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"驚提左之後，佢露到口風俾捉到佢做錯個同事知<br />\n<br />\n到時又好煩，萬一條友死蠢開口講：如果我做錯你同我講我跟翻丫<br />\n<br />\n咁就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都唔想佢被同事暗地排擠既<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3cff4b5016509f92e3570936cbc003cc73ab35","tid":2066772,"uid":27793,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"提<br />\n自己都被同事照顧過<br />\n上司針對或者亂鬧都有<br />\n<br />\n唔會無啦啦對人差，因為你唔會知你放工之後會唔會好抑鬱，有啲人係將工作同個人價值掛鉤<br />\n呢個好危險<br />\n<br />\n至於我係咪懶好心人地有眼睇 要屈要妒忌都無辦法"},{"pid":"3f108d7a35cf234464dbaeb04171393a37c0f6e6","tid":2066772,"uid":29947,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"87689c1e4e2e3da5125b8a3dc4eef0988c6c12ef","tid":2066772,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4aea02c56c904882e75d112e7618f735ea6c3dfd","tid":2066772,"uid":311223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"睇你想多一個朋友定多一個敵人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"驚提左之後，佢露到口風俾捉到佢做錯個同事知<br />\n<br />\n到時又好煩，萬一條友死蠢開口講：如果我做錯你同我講我跟翻丫<br />\n<br />\n咁就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都唔想佢被同事暗地排擠既<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"俾依d人排擠就唔好care啦 全部幼稚撚 <br />\n返工顧住做好自己分內事 唔好參與是非咪得 又唔洗同佢地過人世唔需要咁上心姐 除非你真係覺得唔埋堆唔得<br />\n建議你做自己覺得係正確既嘢"},{"pid":"4d7557a2760f938b4d97f921eef2f079ec9c3a05","tid":2066772,"uid":3935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T20:55:30.000Z","msg":"睇你同事性格<br />\n以前試過做野, 公司個clerk乜9都唔識又比佢發現我識走黎問我要我幫<br />\n之後仲想慢慢將d 野射比我做(我唔係clerk 類staff)<br />\n我唔肯幫佢佢就開始玩小圈子杯9我<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"730ab3aa1ba6870d20119a145b193ca6766b3295","tid":2066772,"uid":118945,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"335539b04d876efc12da291c4d8f9c1ef16bd67c","tid":2066772,"uid":120123,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"都會提返佢。大家出來做野姐.....<br />\n無謂玩到好似宮心計咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T22:17:57.000Z","msg":"你唔想鬥其他人迫住你鬥<br />\n想自保就要鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796b1a609de429062fc3ad379b99bab56fb9f2dd","tid":2066772,"uid":118945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4aea02c56c904882e75d112e7618f735ea6c3dfd","tid":2066772,"uid":311223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"睇你想多一個朋友定多一個敵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T22:18:55.000Z","msg":"提咗唔見得會多個朋友<br />\n可能多幾個敵人"},{"pid":"0bb7e4143f8e4db9c73fdde0077ec6a3eb9b2da0","tid":2066772,"uid":55177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T22:22:56.000Z","msg":"睇咩工， 我就一定提， 提埋其他同事都冇可厚非， 起碼條友再漏都有人執手尾唔會出咩大事"},{"pid":"91418ba00aa7f04009c97e52266313e7b87a97a7","tid":2066772,"uid":101558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T22:33:31.000Z","msg":"提佢老母啦<br />\n次次做完呢樣野就會比人覺得我扮老屎忽教佢<br />\n已經學醒左，除非本身係fd<br />\n一係老細走過黎叫我幫手跟<br />\n唔係既話扮唔知就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後結論，唔想多個敵人就唔好提"},{"pid":"71cbc859556c13513a2156935ff3dbf5cdbb9c60","tid":2066772,"uid":123175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T22:34:48.000Z","msg":"提係為咗大局着想<br />\n希望之後執手尾可以執少啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋提一提就算<br />\n即使真係出咗事都唔會提返<br />\n<br />\n唔係怕人以為我擺款"},{"pid":"01b11a665d5d3e5856e306fdf1eedfa1ced45fdd","tid":2066772,"uid":101558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71cbc859556c13513a2156935ff3dbf5cdbb9c60","tid":2066772,"uid":123175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T22:34:48.000Z","msg":"提係為咗大局着想<br />\n希望之後執手尾可以執少啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋提一提就算<br />\n即使真係出咗事都唔會提返<br />\n<br />\n唔係怕人以為我擺款"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T22:40:45.000Z","msg":"見咁多人話大局著想<br />\n其實唔需要咁著緊咩大局<br />\n首先就係如果對方係小氣閪<br />\n嬲既係你一個<br />\n之後煩既係你一個<br />\n但大圍收皮既大把人幫手<br />\n攤分風險<br />\n再講，就算出事都唔會死得人啦<br />\n如果老細見佢on99都比死得人既野佢做<br />\n咁係老細on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0e33fd58885ed9484ee4c11fac5b41f8cc0760","tid":2066772,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f108d7a35cf234464dbaeb04171393a37c0f6e6","tid":2066772,"uid":29947,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"87689c1e4e2e3da5125b8a3dc4eef0988c6c12ef","tid":2066772,"uid":130466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4aea02c56c904882e75d112e7618f735ea6c3dfd","tid":2066772,"uid":311223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"睇你想多一個朋友定多一個敵人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"驚提左之後，佢露到口風俾捉到佢做錯個同事知<br />\n<br />\n到時又好煩，萬一條友死蠢開口講：如果我做錯你同我講我跟翻丫<br />\n<br />\n咁就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas